The '''1979 [[Prague Skate]]''' was held in November 1979.<ref name=RPA791112/><ref name=Impartial791113/> Medals were awarded in the disciplines of [[single skating|men's singles, ladies' singles]], [[pair skating]], and [[ice dancing]].
