'''''Erdélyi Napló''''' is a [[Hungarian language]] [[right-wing]] weekly published in [[Bihor County|Bihor]],<ref>{{cite book|title=The Europa World Year: Kazakhstan - Zimbabwe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gP_-8rXzQs8C&pg=PA3527|accessdate=10 May 2016|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-85743-255-8|page=3527}}</ref> and distributed nationally throughout [[Transylvania]].<ref>{{cite book|author=Rogers Brubaker|title=Nationalist Politics and Everyday Ethnicity in a Transylvanian Town|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Zgg6eqKKkbcC&pg=PA387|accessdate=10 May 2016|year=2006|publisher=Princeton University Press|isbn=0-691-12834-0|page=387}}</ref>

